<i>noun</i>: 학습자 [학씁짜], 학생 [학쌩] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>학습자 [학씁짜]</dt><br>
<dd>learner; student</dd><br>
<dd>배워서 익히는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who learns by studying something.</dd><br>
<dt>학생 [학쌩]</dt><br>
<dd>student; learner</dd><br>
<dd>학교에 다니면서 공부하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who studies in a school.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>